results.title: Blink membership opens on Blackpink's Weverse
results.snippet: Fans who wish to subscribe to Blackpink's space can do so by filling out necessary information in the Weverse Shop app, according to the group's agency YG Entertainment. Previously, members of Blink could only join Blackpink's Weverse community during certain time periods, but now, there are no time restrictions.Dec 16, 2021
